-22>{{cite web | url=https://www.f4wonline.com/japan/njpwcmll-fantastica-mania-recap-brothers-tag-tournament-finals-250291 | title=NJPW/CMLL Fantastica Mania recap: Brothers tag tournament finals | date=January 23, 2018 | accessdate=October 27, 2018 | first=Ethan | last=Renner | work=[[Wrestling Observer|Wrestling Observer Figure Four Online]]}}</ref>\n|hide=all\n\n|stip1=[[Tag Team]] match\n|match1=[[Fuego (wrestler)|Fuego]] and [[Ryusuke Taguchi]] defeated [[Disturbio]] and [[Puma King|Puma]]\n|time1=08:52\n\n|stip2=[[Professional wrestling tag team match types#Multiple men teamed matches|Eight-man tag team match]]\n|match2=[[Chaos (professional wrestling)|Chaos]] ([[Rocky Romero]], [[Sho Tanaka|SHO]] and [[Yohei Komatsu|YOH]]) and [[Shigeo Okumura|Okumura]] (with [[Mima Shimoda]]) defeated [[Kushida (wrestler)|KUSHIDA]], [[Jushin Thunder Liger]], [[Star Jr.]] and [[Tiger Mask IV|Tiger Mask]]\n|time2=10:59\n\n|stip3=CMLL Brothers Tag Tournament third place match\n|match3=''Nueva Generacion Dinaita'' ([[El Cuatrero]] and [[Sans\u00f3n (wrestler)|Sans\u00f3n]]) defeated [[\u00c1ngel de Oro]] and [[Niebla Roja]]\n|time3=09:30\n\n|stip4=[[Tag Team]] match\n|match4=[[B\u00e1rbaro Cavernario]] and [[Gedo (wrestler)|Gedo]] defeated [[Atlantis (wrestler)|Atlantis]] and [[Hirai Kawato]]\n|time4=09:14\n\n|stip5=[[Professional wrestling tag team match types#Multiple men teamed matches|Six-man tag team match]]\n|match5=[[Los Ingobernables de Japon]] ([[Tetsuya Bushi|BUSHI]], [[Hiromu Takahashi]] and [[Tetsuya Naito]]) defeated [[Drone (wrestler)|Drone]], [[Soberano Jr.]] and [[Volador Jr.]]\n|time5=08:37\n\n|stip6=[[Professional wrestling match types#Variations of singles matches|Singles match]]\n|match6=[[Rush (wrestler)|Rush]] defeated [[Satoshi Kojima]]\n|time6=10:11\n\n|stip7=CMLL Brothers Tag Tournament final match\n|match7=[[Gran Guerrero]] and [[\u00daltimo Guerrero]] defeated [[Dragon Lee (wrestler)|Dragon Lee]] and [[M\u00edstico II|M\u00edstico]]\n|time7=18:42\n\n}}