]] \u2013 poet and critic\n*[[Diana Ross (author)|Diana Ross]] \u2013 children's author (''The Little Red Engine'')\n*[[Erik Routley]] \u2013 hymn writer\n*[[William Bell Scott]] \u2013 poet and [[Pre-Raphaelite Brotherhood|Pre-Raphaelite]] painter\n*[[Freddy Shepherd]] \u2013 businessman and football club chairman \n*[[Jon Silkin]] \u2013 poet\n*[[Peter Smithson]] \u2013 Stockton-born Modernist architect\n*[[John Snow (physician)|John Snow]] \u2013 anaesthetist and founder of [[epidemiology]]\n*[[Sir James Calvert Spence]] \u2013 paediatrician\n*[[William Thomas Stead]] \u2013 journalist \n*[[Algernon Charles Swinburne]] \u2013 poet\n*[[Cecil Philip Taylor]] \u2013 playwright\n*[[Gerald Vann]] \u2013 Roman Catholic theologian and philosopher\n*[[Don Warrington]] \u2013 actor\n*[[Bruce Welch]] \u2013 guitarist, singer\n*[[Denise Welch]] \u2013 actress\n*[[John Wesley]] \u2013 founder of [[Methodism]]\n*[[Kevin Whately]] \u2013 actor\n*[[Ludwig Wittgenstein]] \u2013 philosopher\n*[[Yevgeny Zamyatin]] \u2013 Russian novelist, (''[[We (novel)|We]]'')\n}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Lists of English people by location|Newcastle upon Tyne]]\n[[Category:People from Newcastle upon Tyne|*]]\n[[Category:Newcastle upon Tyne-related lists|People]]\n", "name_user": "Voello", "label": "safe", "comment": "Removed vandalism", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_people_from_Newcastle_upon_Tyne"}
